Package io.github.jnodorp.jiffybox

Klasse Build

java.lang.Object
io.github.jnodorp.jiffybox.Build
public final class Build extends Object
This class contains a static factory method to create a monitoring check builder factory. This is used to build the data needed to create or duplicate monitoring checks.

    • monitoringCheck

      public static MonitoringCheckBuilderFactory monitoringCheck(String name, String ip, Integer port)
      Create a new monitoring check builder factory. All parameters may be 'null' if used for duplication and the according fields need to be preserved.
      Parameter:
      name - The monitoring checks name.
      ip - The monitoring checks ip.
      port - The monitoring checks port.
      Gibt zurück:
      The monitoring check builder factory.
